    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the 'Big Three' preventative measures already addressed: Besian Systems VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with ARP bolts, and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The engine exhibits linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, breathing through factory individual throttle bodies. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, complemented by a limited-slip differential and untouched original paint. No pixel degradation in the electronics or bolster wear on the Nappa leather; this is a turn-key analog masterpiece for the serious purist.",
